reviewText:
A truly fantastic game;
Loved it on the XBOX && still love it;

Just don't expect much improvement in the graphics department;

I'm very happy to confirm that the game works on:

Windows XP Professional 32-bit SP3
Intel Core i3 2120 @ 3.30GHz
4.00GB Dual-Channel DDR3 @ 665MHz
Intel HD Graphics (Intel)

Highly recommended game w/ a great story, if one's never played it before;
If one's already played it, do note that the remastered version does not really offer
anything than the initially released version of the game;

Still, it's fun to play the game once more;

